<br>
Should something be done at Verants end to speed things up? I deffinitely think so.<br>
<br>
No-one is going to read this but here goes -<br>
- You can't predict what FFA will be like becuase it has never happening.  We are a completely different community then any other in EQ. Yes there will be arguments but no more stupid ones than we have now. Will we desolve into anarchy and flick the switch and turn MT into a PvP server? Not on your life.<br>
- I put forth that if RF remains on rotation that Faydedar (Druid), Shissar(Chanter), Magi P'tasa (Mage), Sev (Warrior), Gore (Bard), General (Rogue) and others all go to lists also. I would have said VS for Wiz but he is already BUT for a whole different reason, so I say move him to a list by Wiz instead of guild.<br>
- FFA will be there to make sure that the majority who get their epics will be heavy players in the community.  As of now all you need to do is buy up someone on the list when they leave the game or get your Alt on the list and bam you get your epic handed to you, it may take a bit of time but you'll get it.<br>
<br>
I liken this situation to a  quote from &quot;A Knights Tale&quot;<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;How did the nobles become noble in the first place ........  They took it ..... at the point of a sword.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
This doesn't mean ganking, it means using your strengths and resourcefulness to came out on top in a knightly manner.  The epics are meant to be a status symbol, this list cheapens that status.  Instead of a cleric saying &quot;Yes I rallied my guild together in record time and we worked like a well oiled machine to react faster than those who opposed us&quot; the only thing you get is &quot;Yeah, my time has come to be your rez B*tch come help me&quot;<br>
<br>
If you don't wish to at least try FFA for a short period of time to see how much you hate it, than at least look into these lottery schemes people have suggested.  Why not have a chance for a cleric at the bottom of the list to rise up in the ranks.  It will give them hope of getting there epic before hell freezes over.<br>
<br>
P.S. These are my own personal thoughts and have nothing to do with my guild in the list.<br>
<br>
