<br>
Yes the list is frelling long, but here is a question for you all...CAN YOU STAY UP FOR UP TO 7 DAYS WITH NO SLEEP???  That is the maximum he can normally take to spawn.  I don't know about the rest of you, I can't do that.  I would rather be awake to fight such a mob, and have everyone with me awake, that way no mistakes will be made (yes deaths will occur fighting such mobs, but this way there are down a lot more rather than having people at the keyboard half asleep fighting).  Yes it sucks that the list is so long, but I would rather have to wait on a list, then have it yanked 5 min before my force comes along to help.  I have seen how some of the people (not all and not the majority, but enough) are when it comes to loot and mobs, I would rather not have to fight just to complete something that takes a very long time to complete.<br>
<br>
And for those of you that are complaining that clerics have it so easy for their epic, some of us go out of their way to rez someone...even if they are halfway around Norrath, with no thought for what we will get out of it (though donations are always nice).<br>
<br>
Just for everyone's information, I still have a long way to go before I am on this list.  I really don't like the idea of having to wait over a year or two before I can finally get my epic, but I would rather have to wait than fight everyone on the server for it.  Yes I do have alts, but my cleric will always be my main.<br>
<br>
Well, just my 2cp worth<br>
